snippet.title: Basically Trending
snippet.description:
Hi guys, so my name is Basically Trending and I'm 17. On my channel I try to make entertaining content on Trending topics (hence the name). I'm fairly new on YouTube and I try to make every video better than the last. My content is quite varied but hopefully there is something for everyone here on the channel.

I try to upload content 2/3 times a week.
